&lt;p&gt;Some more indieweb discovery sites to add to the pile mentioned in &lt;a href=&#34;TKTK&#34;&gt;Vol. 6, No. 3&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.blogsareback.com/&#34;&gt;Blogs Are Back&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://blogosphere.app/&#34;&gt;Blogosphere&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://powrss.com/&#34;&gt;powRSS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://scour.ing/&#34;&gt;Scour&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
