&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://player.rss.com/podloser/2932824?theme=light&amp;v=2&amp;share=false&amp;about=false&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;202px&#34; title=&#34;Capitalism for Losers&#34; frameBorder=&#34;0&#34; allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&#34; allowfullscreen scrolling=&#34;no&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://rss.com/podcasts/podloser/2932824/&#34;&gt;Capitalism for Losers | RSS.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;mark&gt;Featuring: Mekons, Queen of Japan, John Cale, Superorganism, shame, Stereophonics, Golomb, media puzzle, Elton Motello, Wanda Jackson, Those Naughty Lumps, Jerskin Fendrix, The Last Dinner Party, A-F-R-O, KEG, Fiona Apple, girl in red, and Underworld w/ Iggy Pop.&lt;/mark&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
