&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;art&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/dwwbmrctk/image/upload/q_auto/f_auto/v1782074889/820DD2CF-6E96-4858-BEF2-940B2CCF55ED_d0c92l.jpg&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;456&#34; alt=&#34;Reseaux des stoppages, Marcel Duchamp, 1914&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.wikiart.org/en/marcel-duchamp/network-of-stoppages-1914&#34;&gt;Reseaux des stoppages&lt;/a&gt;, Marcel Duchamp, 1914&lt;/p&gt;
