&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have come down with shingles. On my face. It sucks. One more mixtape to come, but otherwise Pop Loser is officially entering torpor until March. Have a wonderful holiday season. Rest up. Next year is going to be a big one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
