&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/uploads/2025/i-assure-you-im-not-having-any-fun-at-all.mp3&#34;&gt;I Assure You I’m Not Having Any Fun At All&lt;/a&gt;, a mixtape. (&lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/podcast.xml&#34;&gt;Podcast feed&lt;/a&gt;.) &lt;mark&gt;NOTE:&lt;/mark&gt; Old tapes are archived &lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/details/pod-loser-love&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;mark&gt;Featuring: Queens Of the Stone Age, Viagra Boys, Young Fathers, Lyrics Born, Santigold, Anamanaguchi, Problem Patterns, The Caezars, The Smiths, shower curtain, Eric’s Trip, Fugazi, The Vaselines, Laura Jane Grace, Hot Hot Heat, HotWax, The Wombats.&lt;/mark&gt; Cassette via &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.tapedeck.org/&#34;&gt;TapeDeck.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;heading-20&#34; --&gt;

