&lt;p&gt;&lt;mark&gt;Featuring: Full Flower Moon Band, Nick Waterhouse, Ebba Åsman, Foxwarren, Tropical Fuck Storm, Galaxie 500, The Submarines, The Brian Jonestown Massacre, Young Fathers, Joshua Idehen, Okay Kaya, niina, Bob Vylan, Anyl and the Sniffers, Sharp Pins, Ghost Train Orchestra, and Michael Hurley.&lt;/mark&gt; Cassette via &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.tapedeck.org/&#34;&gt;TapeDeck.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
