&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/uploads/2025/whats-up-doc-holliday.mp3&#34;&gt;What’s Up Doc Holliday&lt;/a&gt;, a mixtape. (&lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/podcast.xml&#34;&gt;Podcast feed&lt;/a&gt;.) &lt;mark&gt;NOTE:&lt;/mark&gt; Old tapes are archived &lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/details/pod-loser-love&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;mark&gt;Featuring: Ennio Morricone, De La Soul, Pan Amsterdam, Ringo Starr, The Beatles, Muddy Waters, Booga Sugar, Mel Tormé, The Pleasure Seekers, Fiona Apple, New Orthodox, Nirvana, Fine Young Cannibals, Leron Thomas, Fcukers, and Skeewiff.&lt;/mark&gt; Cassette via &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.tapedeck.org/&#34;&gt;TapeDeck.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
