&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/uploads/2025/look-at-me-now.mp3&#34;&gt;Look At Me (Now)&lt;/a&gt;, a mixtape. (&lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/podcast.xml&#34;&gt;Podcast feed&lt;/a&gt;.) &lt;mark&gt;NOTE:&lt;/mark&gt; Old tapes are archived &lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/details/pod-loser-love&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;mark&gt;Featuring: Young Fathers, Homeboy Sandman, Chuck E. Weiss, Blossom Dearie, Tune-Yards, The Limiñanas, Benjamin Booker, Laura Jane Grace, Bad Brains, Danny Brown, Bikini Body, Lambrini Girls, Father Of Peace, Smerz, Chicks On Speed, Lena Deluxe, Grateful Dead, and The Miracles.&lt;/mark&gt; Cassette via &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.tapedeck.org/&#34;&gt;TapeDeck.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
