&lt;p&gt;I’ve been sitting on this post for three weeks, adding almost nothing to it. It’s so old, there’s a link to Brian Wilson’s obit. I could take it out, but I didn’t. Why? It’s summer. Go away. See you in the fall.&lt;/p&gt;
