&lt;h4 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Confusions.
  &lt;a href=&#34;#confusions-9&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;
    stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;
    &lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;9&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;15&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;15&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;10&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;8&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;16&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;14&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;🤖 My couples retreat with 3 AI chatbots and &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.wired.com/story/couples-retreat-with-3-ai-chatbots-and-humans-who-love-them-replika-nomi-chatgpt/&#34;&gt;the humans who love them&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;mark&gt;❝The problem with the trip, in the end, was that I’d spent a lot of time imagining all the ways this getaway might seem normal and very little time imagining all the ways it might not. And so, on the second day of the trip, when things started to fall apart, I didn’t know what to say or do.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / 🌳 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mysteryfleshpitnationalpark.com&#34;&gt;Mystery Flesh Pit National Park&lt;/a&gt;. / 🔤 &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://mw.rat.bz/wgterm/&#34;&gt;WarGames&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; terminal fonts. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads&#34;&gt;Nerd Fonts&lt;/a&gt;. / 📱 &lt;a href=&#34;https://endlessdoomscroller.com&#34;&gt;The Endless Doomscroller&lt;/a&gt;. / 🗞️ Combine feeds with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.rssrssrssrss.com&#34;&gt;rssrssrss.com&lt;/a&gt;. / 😱 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Pankajtanwarbanna/scream-to-unlock&#34;&gt;Scream to unlock&lt;/a&gt;. / 📻 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.monkeon.co.uk/wikiradio/&#34;&gt;Wiki Radio&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://musicforprogramming.net&#34;&gt;Music For Programming&lt;/a&gt; (and other things, too). / 🤼 The search for &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ekh67I6wRB0&#34;&gt;Bret Hart vs. Tom Magee&lt;/a&gt;. / 🐸 How &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t86ZjhGxwAY&#34;&gt;Muppets&lt;/a&gt; break free. / 🎙️ There will never be another &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://defector.com/there-will-never-be-another-wtf-with-marc-maron&#34;&gt;WTF with Marc Maron&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. / 🎾 The art of &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.garros.gallery/&#34;&gt;Roland-Garros&lt;/a&gt;. / 🧟‍♂️ Zombie &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mOV0BV45NqA&#34;&gt;Family Circus&lt;/a&gt;. / 🕹️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://bbenchoff.github.io/pages/FiniteAtari.html&#34;&gt;Finite Atari Machine&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;mark&gt;❝This project answers a question no one asked, no one wanted, and is a massive waste of resources: What if I shove a billion monkeys in a GPU and asked them to write a game for the Atari 2600?❞&lt;/mark&gt; / 🖥️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://absurd.website&#34;&gt;absurd.website&lt;/a&gt;. / ⚱️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nytimes.com/2025/06/11/arts/music/brian-wilson-dead.html&#34;&gt;Brian Wilson&lt;/a&gt; died.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;heading-39&#34; --&gt;

