&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;💻 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.newyorker.com/culture/open-questions/are-we-living-in-the-age-of-info-determinism&#34;&gt;Info-determinism&lt;/a&gt; and the ruin of society. (I added the &amp;ldquo;ruin&amp;rdquo; bit.) &lt;mark&gt;❝Until very recently, the cultural cocoon we lived in was woven by other humans. Going forward, it will be increasingly designed by computers.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / &lt;a href=&#34;https://onemillionscreenshots.com&#34;&gt;One Million Screenshots&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.twitter-95.com&#34;&gt;Twitter &amp;lsquo;95&lt;/a&gt;. / Is Ben &lt;a href=&#34;https://stuckinthescroll.com&#34;&gt;scrolling TikTok&lt;/a&gt; right now? / &lt;a href=&#34;https://playhtml.fun/fridge.html&#34;&gt;The internet&amp;rsquo;s fridge&lt;/a&gt;. / 🗄️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.radioshackcatalogs.com&#34;&gt;Radio Shack Catalogs&lt;/a&gt; (dot com). / &lt;a href=&#34;https://blog.archive.org/2024/07/10/new-ways-to-search-archived-music-news/&#34;&gt;MTV News&lt;/a&gt; is now preserved and searchable. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://public.work&#34;&gt;Public Work&lt;/a&gt;, a search engine for public domain content. / &lt;a href=&#34;http://peoplesgdarchive.org&#34;&gt;The People&amp;rsquo;s Graphic Design Archive&lt;/a&gt;. / A complete visual guide to &lt;a href=&#34;https://obsoletesony.substack.com/p/complete-visual-guide-to-sony-minidisc&#34;&gt;Sony MiniDisc Blank Media&lt;/a&gt; (1992-2004). / 🎨 Did &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.thecollector.com/did-marcel-duchamp-plagiarize-famous-work/&#34;&gt;Duchamp&lt;/a&gt; steal his urinal? / 📰 &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.billboard.com/pro/spin-magazine-returns-print-editor-in-chief-bob-guccione-jr/&#34;&gt;SPIN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.forbes.com/sites/susannahbreslin/2024/08/08/playboy-to-bring-back-its-print-magazine-with-annual-edition/&#34;&gt;Playboy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt; are returning to print. Music and pornography on the internet will plod along mostly not noticing. / 👾 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.whatbeatsrock.com&#34;&gt;What beats rock&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
