&lt;p&gt;📰 The death of &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nytimes.com/2024/09/09/business/red-lobster-seafood-downfall.html&#34;&gt;Red Lobster&lt;/a&gt;. / How &lt;a href=&#34;https://thewalrus.ca/moleskine/&#34;&gt;Moleskine&lt;/a&gt; won in the digital era. / This &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.newstatesman.com/long-reads/kate-mossman-interview/2024/07/slavoj-zizek-the-court-jester-of-late-capitalism&#34;&gt;Žižek profile&lt;/a&gt; veers into sex way more than you&amp;rsquo;d think or necessarily want. &lt;mark&gt;❝He has brought me an umbrella; he also has his own – he pats his top pocket – which in Žižek language is “of anal [pronounced annal] character”, meaning compact and easy to hide.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / 🗄️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.romhacking.net&#34;&gt;ROMhacking.net&lt;/a&gt; is shutting down (&lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/details/romhacking.net-20240801&#34;&gt;Archive&lt;/a&gt;). / &lt;a href=&#34;https://citizen-dj.labs.loc.gov&#34;&gt;Citizen DJ&lt;/a&gt;. / 📺 &lt;a href=&#34;https://samkriss.substack.com/p/eternity&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Girls&lt;/em&gt; rewatch&lt;/a&gt; as existential crisis. &lt;mark&gt;❝Whatever’s happening isn’t time, it’s just duration, and its only measure is decay.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / 🎨 &lt;a href=&#34;https://paolocirio.net/work/street-ghosts/&#34;&gt;Street Ghosts&lt;/a&gt;. / 💻 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.merklemap.com&#34;&gt;Merklemap&lt;/a&gt;, a subdomain search engine. / Free font: &lt;a href=&#34;https://departuremono.com&#34;&gt;Departure Mono&lt;/a&gt;. / ChatGPT sucks at &lt;a href=&#34;https://ea.rna.nl/2024/05/27/when-chatgpt-summarises-it-actually-does-nothing-of-the-kind/&#34;&gt;summarizing&lt;/a&gt;. / 📱&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.inpress.app&#34;&gt;InPress&lt;/a&gt; is a news app that is also a dating app and the only legit Twitter replacement. /🌜I&amp;rsquo;m going to start operating on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.atlasobscura.com/articles/moon-time-zone&#34;&gt;Moon Time&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
