&lt;h4 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Confusions.
  &lt;a href=&#34;#confusions-7&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;
    stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;
    &lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;9&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;15&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;15&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;10&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;8&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;16&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;14&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;📱Every &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.wheresyoured.at/never-forgive-them/&#34;&gt;digital thing&lt;/a&gt; you touch probably sucks. &lt;mark&gt;❝Our digital lives are actively abusive and hostile, riddled with subtle and overt cons. Our apps are ever-changing, adapting not to our needs or conditions, but to the demands of investors and internal stakeholders that have reduced who we are and what we do to an ever-growing selection of manipulatable metrics. It isn’t that you don’t “get” tech, it’s that the tech you use every day is no longer built for you, and as a result feels a very specific kind of insane.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / 📰 Classic: &lt;a href=&#34;https://harpers.org/archive/1941/08/who-goes-nazi/&#34;&gt;Who goes Nazi?&lt;/a&gt; / 🌎 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2024/dec/12/tiktok-carbon-footprint&#34;&gt;Ban TikTok&lt;/a&gt;. / ⛓️‍💥 &lt;a href=&#34;https://publicdomainreview.org/features/entering-the-public-domain/2025/&#34;&gt;Public domain 2025&lt;/a&gt; kicks off with &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1hsxK0UMlQ&#34;&gt;Popeye the Slayer Man&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. / 🍿 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nightflightplus.com&#34;&gt;Night Flight Plus&lt;/a&gt;. (&lt;a href=&#34;https://pitchfork.com/thepitch/how-80s-subculture-staple-night-flight-was-reborn-as-a-punk-and-horror-streaming-network/&#34;&gt;Story&lt;/a&gt;.) / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fo/iozg1gm9snx2oq4bza4jd/AGawAwstU24C6xoEpRe-Sgw?rlkey=vgzm9k3f1m19c6406j892o0py&amp;e=3&amp;dl=0&#34;&gt;Star Wars Grindhouse&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.newyorker.com/humor/shouts-murmurs/is-it-a-movie-or-a-film&#34;&gt;Movie or film?&lt;/a&gt; / ⚱️ The &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/amazing-kreskin-dead-1.7407334&#34;&gt;Amazing Kreskin&lt;/a&gt; died. / ♟️ I’ve been training for &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2024/dec/12/tiktok-carbon-footprint&#34;&gt;Open the Microwave&lt;/a&gt; my whole life. / Every &lt;a href=&#34;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nkHWqYre866xihxN3MnHr5YFzY4gQWDT/edit?pli=1&#34;&gt;board game rulebook&lt;/a&gt; sucks. / 🎛️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/@knobfeel&#34;&gt;Feelin’ knobs&lt;/a&gt; for content. / 🖥️&lt;a href=&#34;https://mac-pet.com/&#34;&gt;Mac Pet&lt;/a&gt; is cute. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://infinitestroll.com/&#34;&gt;Infinite Stroll&lt;/a&gt; is soothing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
