&lt;p&gt;There is no rhyme or reason to the volume structure here other than I like counting things and it builds in breaks I can take basically whenever. Baseball was starting, thus ending Vol. 1 so I could do some fantasy drafting and watch a lot of games. But that’s all done, and after &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mlb.com/news/blue-jays-no-hit-by-ronel-blanco-astros&#34;&gt;yesterday&lt;/a&gt; I may never watch another baseball game again anyway, so let’s get on with number two.&lt;/p&gt;
