&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;robot-rot-and-other-confusions&#34; --&gt;

&lt;h4 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Robot rot (and other confusions).
  &lt;a href=&#34;#robot-rot-and-other-confusions&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;
    stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;
    &lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;9&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;15&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;15&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;10&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;8&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;16&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;14&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;♟️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.businessinsider.com/sexism-cheating-nightclubs-internet-inside-dark-heart-modern-chess-toxic-2024-5&#34;&gt;Chess on the internet&lt;/a&gt; is mostly like everything else on the internet: predictably awful. &lt;mark&gt;❝Chess&amp;rsquo; problems aren&amp;rsquo;t unique. But it is uniquely positioned to act as an accelerant for the internet&amp;rsquo;s worst impulses: sexism, abuse, cheating, elitism, and toxic nerdery.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / Related: &lt;a href=&#34;https://nymag.com/intelligencer/article/hans-niemann-chess-championship-cheating-scandal-interview.html&#34;&gt;Everybody hates Hans&lt;/a&gt;. / Less related: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/2024/05/15/scrabble-anonymous/&#34;&gt;Scrabble, Anonymous&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;mark&gt;❝The unwilling, unconscious anagramming of words is the primary side effect of a life devoted to Scrabble. This is ultimately what the game is about: memorizing words with no concern for their meaning.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / 🍿 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL30RAv-0lkxHdTcoGGgx5L6eXIHnnrEHC&#34;&gt;3,000 free movies&lt;/a&gt; on YouTube. / Roger Corman&amp;rsquo;s &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://youtu.be/oA7LcG4ch3A?si=Bc-JUR_F1iahg4-r&#34;&gt;Fantastic Four&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://film-grab.com&#34;&gt;Filmgrab&lt;/a&gt;, collected stills from films. / 💻 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2021/08/dead-internet-theory-wrong-but-feels-true/619937/?ref=404media.co&#34;&gt;Dead internet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.404media.co/facebooks-ai-spam-isnt-the-dead-internet-its-the-zombie-internet/&#34;&gt;zombie internet&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://futurism.com/advon-ai-content&#34;&gt;vampire internet&lt;/a&gt;, oh my. / Related: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.pewresearch.org/data-labs/2024/05/17/when-online-content-disappears/&#34;&gt;Rotting internet&lt;/a&gt;. / Also related: The ruin of &lt;a href=&#34;https://slate.com/technology/2024/05/deviantart-what-happened-ai-decline-lawsuit-stability.html&#34;&gt;DeviantArt&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://udm14.com&#34;&gt;Google&lt;/a&gt; fixed. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://perthirtysix.com/communal-plot-daily-poll&#34;&gt;The Communal Plot&lt;/a&gt;, a daily visualization we all build together. / 🛻 Have you seen a &lt;a href=&#34;https://defector.com/have-you-seen-a-cybertruck-yet&#34;&gt;Cybertruck&lt;/a&gt; yet? &lt;mark&gt;❝If there is anything to take away from this, it is that I once had an attribute that might have allowed me to make it extremely big in the contemporary automotive industry, which is &amp;ldquo;acting like a precocious doofus child while saying possibly-false car-related stuff in a way that favorably inclined observers found compelling.&amp;rdquo; That can get you pretty far in the industry. I know this in a way that I didn&amp;rsquo;t just a few days ago, because, finally, I have seen a Tesla Cybertruck with my own eyes.❞&lt;/mark&gt; / ⚾ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nytimes.com/2024/05/21/sports/toronto-blue-jays-fan-foul-ball.html&#34;&gt;Hero&lt;/a&gt;. / 📺 &lt;a href=&#34;https://youtu.be/nkOQ46F8MbQ?si=-_FnGY2F9ttZL5Mf&#34;&gt;Harmony Korine&lt;/a&gt; on Letterman. / 📱 Point your phone at your Lego and &lt;a href=&#34;https://brickit.app&#34;&gt;Brickit&lt;/a&gt; will design stuff to build.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;heading-17&#34; --&gt;

