&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://longreads.com/2024/01/16/beauty-and-the-beat-book-excerpt-lisa-whittington-hill/&#34;&gt;An excerpt from Beauty and the Beat&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;mark&gt;❝When the Go-Go’s heard Beauty and the Beat for the first time they cried, but they weren’t exactly tears of joy. &lt;strong&gt;They thought they were making a punk record&lt;/strong&gt;.❞&lt;/mark&gt; Buy Friend Lisa’s &lt;a href=&#34;https://bookshop.org/p/books/the-go-go-s-beauty-and-the-beat-lisa-whittington-hill/19219481&#34;&gt;new book&lt;/a&gt; about the Go-Go’s (or her &lt;a href=&#34;https://alllitup.ca/books/girls-interrupted/&#34;&gt;other new book&lt;/a&gt; about the failures of pop culture).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
