&lt;p&gt;📱 &lt;a href=&#34;https://daftsocial.com&#34;&gt;Daft Social&lt;/a&gt;, the anti-social social network for minimalists. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.pi.fyi&#34;&gt;Perfectly Imperfect&lt;/a&gt;, which I’m &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.pi.fyi/u/poploser&#34;&gt;using&lt;/a&gt; to try and understand the youngs. / Swipe right to add me to your professional network &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.businessinsider.com/linkedin-is-a-dating-app-remote-work-online-romance-2024-1&#34;&gt;on LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;mark&gt;❝The common thread for love-hijacked social-media sites is a single feature: DMs.❞&lt;/mark&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
