&lt;h4 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Art fool confidential.
  &lt;a href=&#34;#art-fool-confidential&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;
    stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;
    &lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;9&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;15&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;15&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;10&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;8&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;16&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;14&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The story of the very real and authenticated &lt;a href=&#34;https://1ft.io/proxy?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fmagazine%2Farchive%2F2024%2F03%2Forlando-art-museum-basquiat-forgeries%2F677171%2F&#34;&gt;Basquiats found in a locker&lt;/a&gt; and sold for bundles. &lt;mark&gt;❝The new owners gradually amassed evidence to suggest that the works were authentic: a forensic analysis by a handwriting expert, an in-depth report by a Basquiat scholar, and a statement of authenticity signed by a founding member of a committee that the Basquiat estate had established to vet potential forgeries.❞&lt;/mark&gt; Reader, they were not real. / 🎨 Great headline: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2024/01/oligarchs-art-collectors-billionaires-money-picasso-free-ports/&#34;&gt;Monet changes everything&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://artsandculture.google.com/pocketgallery/1QVRSOcHMzQMmQ&#34;&gt;All the Vermeers&lt;/a&gt;. / &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.richardjohnson.ca/ice-huts&#34;&gt;Canada&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.thisiscolossal.com/2024/01/richard-johnson-ice-huts/&#34;&gt;(via)&lt;/a&gt; / AI-generated &lt;a href=&#34;https://pixel-art.ai&#34;&gt;pixel art&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;&#34; --&gt;

&lt;h3 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
