&lt;p&gt;I was the tech critic at &lt;em&gt;This Magazine&lt;/em&gt; for six years. Some of those columns are here, along with select published pieces from recent(ish) years.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;heading&#34; --&gt;

