&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;tech-stuff&#34; --&gt;

&lt;h4 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;Tech stuff.
  &lt;a href=&#34;#tech-stuff&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor-link&#34;&gt;
&lt;svg
    xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;
    width=&#34;1rem&#34; height=&#34;1rem&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;
    stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;
    stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;
    &lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;9&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;4&#34; y1=&#34;15&#34; x2=&#34;20&#34; y2=&#34;15&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;10&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;8&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;16&#34; y1=&#34;3&#34; x2=&#34;14&#34; y2=&#34;21&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As of July 2026, this website is powered by &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; using a modified version of &lt;a href=&#34;https://kaiiiz.github.io/hugo-theme-monochrome/&#34;&gt;Monochrome&lt;/a&gt; and hosted on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/poploser/tylerhellard.com&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;. The type is set primarily in &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vernnobile/mondaFont&#34;&gt;Monda&lt;/a&gt; with icons, including the many skulls, come from &lt;a href=&#34;https://fontawesome.com/&#34;&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/a&gt;. Basic stats are collected with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.goatcounter.com/&#34;&gt;GoatCounter&lt;/a&gt; (most options turned off — I&amp;rsquo;m only getting basic page views and some limited referral data). All content is written and edited in markdown with &lt;a href=&#34;https://ia.net/writer&#34;&gt;IA Writer&lt;/a&gt;. Here are your &lt;span style=&#34;color: #fff; background: #FE5C00; padding: 0 5px;&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RSS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; options: 🚒 &lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/feed.xml&#34;&gt;Firehose&lt;/a&gt; (blog posts, other writing, mixtapes, photos, etc.) / 📰 &lt;a href=&#34;https://tylerhellard.com/poploser.xml&#34;&gt;Pop Loser&lt;/a&gt; (just the blog posts) / 🎧 &lt;a href=&#34;https://media.rss.com/podloser/feed.xml&#34;&gt;Pod Loser&lt;/a&gt; (a podcast feed for just the mixtapes).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
&lt;!-- begin-chunk data-anchor=&#34;heading-2&#34; --&gt;

&lt;h3 class=&#34;header-anchor-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-skull-crossbones&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
