&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A journal of innumerable confusions.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pop Loser is a collection of half-thoughts, links and mixtapes sorta about technology, media, arts and culture. &lt;a href=&#34;/poploser/&#34;&gt;Volume 6&lt;/a&gt; is now in progress.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;mark&gt;Collected:&lt;/mark&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;/poploser/vol1&#34;&gt;Vol. 1&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;/poploser/vol2&#34;&gt;Vol. 2&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;/poploser/vol3&#34;&gt;Vol. 3&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;/poploser/vol4&#34;&gt;Vol. 4&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;/poploser/vol4&#34;&gt;Vol. 5&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;mark&gt;Also:&lt;/mark&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;/mixtapes/&#34;&gt;Mixtapes&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;/feed.xml&#34;&gt;RSS&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://media.rss.com/podloser/feed.xml&#34;&gt;Podcast&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- end-chunk --&gt;
